column2: The Nimble Fighter is a capable and proficient fighter.
The Immortal Warlord is believed to be un-killable on the battlefield.
The Simple Jack is jack of all trades and master of none.
This character was raised in a city - this character is especially mindful of various monetary situations of many.
This character was raised in a temple - this character knows the difference between virtues and sins. However, following said virtues still may prove to be difficult.
